&+&\alpha_1 2^{-\frac{n}{2}}\sum_{x\in \mathbb{Z}^n_2}(-1)^{a_0(x)\oplus a_{2}(x)\oplus u\cdot x}+\alpha_2 2^{-\frac{n}{2}}\sum_{x\in \mathbb{Z}^n_2}(-1)^{a_1(x)\oplus a_{2}(x)\oplus u\cdot x}\\
&+&\alpha_32^{-\frac{n}{2}}\sum_{x\in \mathbb{Z}^n_2}(-1)^{a_0(x)+a_1(x)+a_{2}(x)\oplus u\cdot x}\\
&=&\alpha_0 W_{a_2}(u)+\alpha_1 W_{a_0+a_2}(u)+\alpha_2 W_{a_1+a_2}(u)+\alpha_3 W_{a_0+a_1+a_2}(u).
\end{eqnarray*}
Note that in Lemma \ref{lemma1}, the common factor $2^{-2}$ of the coefficients $\alpha_i$ is moved to the left-hand side by considering $4\mathcal{H}_f(u)$ instead of $\mathcal{H}_f(u)$. Thus, the coefficients $\alpha_i$ above are identical to those in Lemma \ref{lemma1}.

